OL,3,CGovernment asylum housing plans to
OL,4,Ccost millions more than hotels `
OL,5,Cwatchdog
OL,7,FGovernment plans for asylum
OL,8,Faccommodation, like the Bibby
OL,9,FStockholm barge in Dorset, will cost
OL,10,Ftens of millions of pounds more than
OL,11,Fusing hotels, with flagship sites
OL,12,Fhousing hundreds fewer migrants than
OL,13,Fplanned, Whitehall's spending watchdog
OL,14,Fhas found.
OL,16,FThe National Audit Office (NAO) said
OL,17,Fthe Home Office expects to spend #1.2
OL,18,Fbillion on housing asylum seekers in
OL,19,Flarge accommodation sites and latest
OL,20,Festimates suggest they will cost #46
OL,21,Fmillion more than using hotels.
