OL,3,CGovernment asylum housing plans to
OL,4,Ccost millions more than hotels `
OL,5,Cwatchdog
OL,7,FBy the end of March, the department
OL,8,Fexpects to have spent at least #230
OL,9,Fmillion developing four major projects
OL,10,F` the Bibby Stockholm barge in
OL,11,FPortland, Dorset, the former RAF bases
OL,12,Fat Scampton in Lincolnshire and
OL,13,FWethersfield in Essex, and ex-student
OL,14,Faccommodation in Huddersfield, West
OL,15,FYorkshire.
OL,17,FBut, so far, just two of the sites are
OL,18,Fopen and were only housing around 900
OL,19,Fpeople by the end of January,
OL,20,Faccording to the watchdog's findings.
