OL,4,Ccost millions more than hotels `
OL,5,Cwatchdog
OL,7,FIt comes as ministers have scaled back
OL,8,Fthe number of asylum seekers due to be
OL,9,Fhoused at the former home of the famed
OL,10,F617 "Dambuster" Squadron and the Red
OL,11,FArrows near Lincoln from 2,000 to 800.
OL,13,FThe NAO findings reveal the Home
OL,14,FOffice is also considering cutting the
OL,15,Fmaximum number of migrants housed at
OL,16,FWethersfield.
