OL,7,FThe department pursued the programme
OL,8,Fdespite "repeated" assessments that it
OL,9,F"could not be delivered as planned",
OL,10,FMr Davies warned as he called on the
OL,11,FHome Office to "reflect on lessons
OL,12,Flearned from establishing its large
OL,13,Fsites programme at speed and improve
OL,14,Fco-ordination with central and local
OL,15,Fgovernment given wider housing
OL,16,Fpressures".
