OL,5,Cwatchdog
OL,7,FLabour's shadow home secretary Yvette
OL,8,FCooper branded the findings
OL,9,F"staggering," adding: "The British
OL,10,Ftaxpayer is already paying out eye
OL,11,Fwatering sums on asylum hotels and now
OL,12,Fit turns out the sites they promised
OL,13,Fwould save money are costing the
OL,14,Ftaxpayer even more. Rishi Sunak has
OL,15,Ftaken the Tories' chaos and failure in
OL,16,Fthe asylum system to a new level."
