OL,4,Ccost millions more than hotels `
OL,5,Cwatchdog
OL,7,FChief executive of the Refugee Council
OL,8,FEnver Solomon described it as "another
OL,9,Falarming example of bad policies being
OL,10,Fimplemented badly at huge financial
OL,11,Fand human cost", while Steve Smith,
OL,12,Fthe boss of migrant charity
OL,13,FCare4Calais which is taking legal
OL,14,Faction over the use of Wethersfield
OL,15,Ffor asylum accommodation, added:
OL,16,F"Someone in Government has to be held
OL,17,Faccountable for the fear and trauma
OL,18,Fthey have created."
