OL,4,Ccost millions more than hotels `
OL,5,Cwatchdog
OL,7,F"The Home Office originally assessed
OL,8,Fthat large sites would be around #94
OL,9,Fmillion cheaper than hotels. Its
OL,10,Flatest estimates suggest they will
OL,11,Fcost #46 million more than using
OL,12,Fhotels, although the Home Office
OL,13,Fbelieves they will provide more
OL,14,Fappropriate and sustainable
OL,15,Faccommodation," the watchdog added.
