OL,5,Cwatchdog
OL,7,FAccording to the findings, the Home
OL,8,FOffice originally estimated set-up
OL,9,Fcosts at the former RAF bases would be
OL,10,F#5 million each but they increased to
OL,11,F#49 million for Wethersfield and #27
OL,12,Fmillion for Scampton.
OL,14,FSo far only Wethersfield ` which has a
OL,15,Fcapacity of 1,700 ` and the Bibby
OL,16,FStockholm, with space for around 500
OL,17,Fmen, are housing asylum seekers.
