OL,7,FBut both sites were housing just under
OL,8,Fhalf the number of migrants the Home
OL,9,FOffice expected would be the case at
OL,10,Fthe end of January, with 576 at
OL,11,FWethersfield and 321 on the Bibby
OL,12,Fbarge at that point.
OL,14,FAccording to the report, the Home
OL,15,FOffice is "now considering reducing
OL,16,Fthe maximum number of people it
OL,17,Faccommodates" at Wethersfield but has
OL,18,Fnot confirmed the number.
