OL,7,FThe department expects Scampton to
OL,8,Fstart housing asylum seekers from
OL,9,FApril, with Huddersfield following in
OL,10,FMay, it added.
OL,12,FThe NAO also found:
OL,14,F` Reviews by the Infrastructure and
OL,15,FProjects Authority rated the Home
OL,16,FOffice's work in this area as "red",
OL,17,Fmeaning "successful delivery of the
OL,18,Fprogramme to time, cost and quality
OL,19,Fappears to be unachievable".
