OL,7,F` The Home Office rated its own
OL,8,Fperformance as "red" as it recognised
OL,9,Fthe challenges of the work, repeatedly
OL,10,Frevising accommodation targets
OL,11,F"downwards".
OL,13,F` The department "prioritised awarding
OL,14,Fcontracts quickly, and modifying
OL,15,Fexisting contracts over fully-
OL,16,Fcompetitive tenders", with "overly-
OL,17,Fambitious accommodation timetables"
OL,18,Fleading to "increased procurement
OL,19,Frisks".
