OL,7,F` Emergency planning rules were used
OL,8,Fso sites could be found, and work
OL,9,Fcould begin, quickly before speaking
OL,10,Fto affected communities about the
OL,11,Fplans to "reduce the risk of local
OL,12,Fopposition affecting negotiations". In
OL,13,FJanuary the Home Office was "still
OL,14,Fworking with providers to develop
OL,15,Fspecific measures assessing residents'
OL,16,Fsafety at large sites".
