OL,7,F` The Home Office is "resetting" its
OL,8,Fprogramme and developing a "longer-
OL,9,Fterm accommodation strategy" which
OL,10,Fwill see it reduce the number of
OL,11,Fspaces it intends to provide at such
OL,12,Fsites amid proposals to "identify
OL,13,Fsmaller sites accommodating between
OL,14,F200-700 people". Mr Davies said this
OL,15,Fplan "makes sense".
