OL,5,Cwatchdog
OL,7,F` There are "uncertainties" about how
OL,8,Fthe Illegal Migration Act is being
OL,9,Fimplemented, making it harder for the
OL,10,FHome Office to assess what asylum
OL,11,Faccommodation it needs. The report
OL,12,Fsaid the law changes will make it
OL,13,F"more difficult to assess how much and
OL,14,Fwhat type of accommodation the Home
OL,15,FOffice will need" as it does not know
OL,16,Fhow effective the deterrent will be or
OL,17,Fhow it will affect the amount and type
OL,18,Fof accommodation it needs.
