OL,5,Cwatchdog
OL,7,FOn Monday it emerged that Home Office
OL,8,Fminister Tom Pursglove had confirmed
OL,9,Fin a letter to Gainsborough
OL,10,FConservative MP Sir Edward Leigh that
OL,11,Fthe "regular occupancy" at RAF
OL,12,FScampton would be a maximum of 800
OL,13,Fasylum seekers instead of the original
OL,14,F2,000 men destined for the site which
OL,15,Fhas been beset by legal challenges.
OL,17,FA Home Office spokeswoman said: "While
OL,18,Fthe NAO's figures include set-up
OL,19,Fcosts, it is currently better value
OL,20,Ffor money for the taxpayer to continue
OL,21,Fwith these sites than to use hotels."
