OL,7,FIts efforts mean the cost of hotels
OL,8,Fwill fall, the Home Office promised,
OL,9,Fas it said it was "closing dozens of
OL,10,Fasylum hotels every month", adding:
OL,11,F"But we have further to go, which is
OL,12,Fwhy we are passing the Safety of
OL,13,FRwanda Bill, deterring Channel
OL,14,Fcrossings and get flights off to
OL,15,FRwanda ` because it is only when
OL,16,Fpeople are discouraged from taking
OL,17,Fthose journeys that we can end asylum
OL,18,Fhotel use for good."
